      "span_text": "The mouse monoclonal antibody 2D6 binds to the N-terminus at (G74WVPTR78), which is near the start of transmembrane helix 1 (Supplemental Figure 3) .  The goat polyclonal antibody (C20) maps to the last 12 amino acids of PAR4 (Supplemental Figure 3) ."
